'''Isaac Godfrey Geoffrey Nabwana''', uzwi cyane ku izina rya '''Nabwana IGG''', ni umukinnyi [[Ubugande|wa]] firime muri [[Uganda]] akaba na producer<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm4254419/</ref> .   Uwashinze studio ya firime Wakaliwood, Nabwana azwi cyane kubera urugomo rwubusa muri film ye.  Nabwana yatangiye kwamamara nyuma yo kohereza trailer ya film ye Who Killed Captain Alex? kuri YouTube muri 2010 hanyuma nyuma ya firime nyirizina muri 2015. Filime yabonye umwanya wo gusenga none yicaye kuri miliyoni 6.4 kuri YouTube<ref>https://americancinemathequecalendar.com/category/director/nabwana-igg</ref>.

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Nabwana yavukiye muri [[Uganda]] ku ngoma ya [[Idi Amin Dada|Idi Amin]] mu 1973. Mu ntambara yo muri Uganda Bush, bivugwa ko we na murumuna we birukanywe na kajugujugu . Iyi kajugujugu irashobora kugaragara muri Who Killed Captain Alex?.<ref>https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/nabwana-i-g-g/g11cjp98d77?hl=en</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Nkuko atari yarigeze aba mu ikinamico, yishingikirizaga ahanini kuri barumuna be n'inshuti ibisobanuro bya firime zasohotse mu ikinamico. Yagiye mu masomo yo gusana mudasobwa, ariko ahatirwa kureka ishuri nyuma yukwezi kwa mbere kubera kubura amafaranga<ref>https://cines.com/en/directors/nabwana-i-g-g</ref>. Kubwibyo, yatangiye kwiga gukora firime nibice byayo muburyo bwo kwigira wenyine hamwe nubunararibonye bwe bwo kugerageza-kwibeshya hamwe na kamera nibikoresho byo gutunganya. Afite imyaka 32, yatangiye gukina film nkumwuga. Mu 2005, Nabwana yashinze Ramon Film Productions: izina ryakomotse kuri nyirakuru, Rachel na Monica, nyuma rizwi ku izina rya Wakaliwood<ref>https://mubi.com/cast/nabwana-i-g-g</ref> .   

Ibikorwa bye bya firime bishingiye murugo rwe aho yatangiye gukora no gufata amashusho yindirimbo kuva 2009<ref>https://thefridacinema.org/movies-so-bad-theyre-good/</ref>. Ramon Production yitabiriye firime zirenga 44. Zimwe muri firime zizwi zakozwe na Ramon Productions Who Killed Captain Alex? ,Bad Black, na ''Tebaatusasula'' .   Filime ''Who Killed Captain Alex?'' izwi nka firime yambere yuzuye ibikorwa muri cinema ya [[Uganda]].<ref>https://www.viddy-well.com/reviews/tag/Ramon+Film+Productions</ref> 

Igihe Alan Hofmanis, umuyobozi mukuru mu iserukiramuco rya firime rifite icyicaro mu mujyi wa New York, yagiye muri [[Uganda]], yahuye na Nabwana maze asaba ko yakora documentaire kuri Ramon Film Productions, Hofmanis kuva  ubwo yimukira muri [[Uganda]] kugira ngo afashe kumenyekanisha sinema ya Wakaliwood ku isi. Yahawe kandi gukina filime ya ''Bad Black mu'' mwaka wa 2016 Nabwana kandi yiswe "umukinnyi wa mbere wa filime wa Mzungu Uganda<ref>https://www.claudinecolin.com/en/1910-louis-cyprien-rials-with-ramon-film-productions-on-the-wakaliga-roa-dside-sam-prize-for-contemporary-art-2017</ref>." 

Nabwana yatsindiye  ibihembo 6 

== Uburyo bwo gufata amashusho hamwe ninsanganyamatsiko ==
Nabwana yafashe amashusho ye mu Luganda, imvugo ya Baganda, ubwoko bunini bwa [[Uganda]]. Nabwana azwiho ibikorwa nubugizi bwa nabi bivanze no gusetsa muri film ye. Afata ibyemezo muri firime ye bikabije bigizwe ahanini no kurwanisha imbunda Kung-fu nubuhanzi bwintambara . Nabwana afite kandi ibihangano bye yise 'Video Joker' (cyangwa VJ muri make) kugirango atange ibisobanuro kuri firime aho avuga urwenya no gutaka amagambo adasanzwe. Iyi mico yagaragaye muri firime zose za Nabwana.<ref>https://www.okayafrica.com/crazy-world-the-new-ugandan-action-film-from-wakaliwood/</ref><ref>https://www.sputnikmusic.com/news/41360/Heaven-Shall-Burn-go-to-Wakaliwood/</ref>

